# Tailwind CSS Guidelines

## Brand Token Integration

Use CSS custom properties with Tailwind's arbitrary value syntax:

```html
<!-- Colors -->
<div class="bg-[var(--color-background)] text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
<button class="bg-[var(--color-primary)] hover:bg-[var(--color-primary-light)]">

<!-- Or extend in tailwind.config.mjs -->
```

## Tailwind Config Extension

```js
// tailwind.config.mjs
export default {
  theme: {
    extend: {
      colors: {
        primary: 'var(--color-primary)',
        'primary-light': 'var(--color-primary-light)',
        'primary-dark': 'var(--color-primary-dark)',
        secondary: 'var(--color-secondary)',
        background: 'var(--color-background)',
        surface: 'var(--color-surface)',
        divider: 'var(--color-divider)',
      },
      fontFamily: {
        sans: ['Roboto Flex', 'Helvetica', 'Arial', 'sans-serif'],
      },
      borderRadius: {
        'sm': '8px',
        'md': '12px',
        'lg': '16px',
        'xl': '28px',
      },
    },
  },
}
```

## Component Patterns

### Buttons

```html
<!-- Primary -->
<button class="px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-sm
               hover:bg-primary-light transition-colors duration-150
               focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-light">
  Get Started
</button>

<!-- Secondary -->
<button class="px-6 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-semibold rounded-sm
               hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150">
  Learn More
</button>
```

### Cards

```html
<div class="bg-surface rounded-md p-6 shadow-sm border border-divider">
  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Title</h3>
  <p class="text-[var(--color-text-secondary)] mt-2">Description</p>
</div>
```

### Section Spacing

```html
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Content -->
  </div>
</section>
```

## Responsive Breakpoints

| Breakpoint | Min Width | Usage |
|------------|-----------|-------|
| `sm:` | 640px | Mobile landscape |
| `md:` | 768px | Tablets |
| `lg:` | 1024px | Desktop |
| `xl:` | 1280px | Large desktop |
| `2xl:` | 1536px | Extra large |

## Dark Mode

```html
<!-- Uses data attribute, not class -->
<html data-theme="dark">

<!-- Styles respond automatically via CSS variables -->
<div class="bg-background text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">
  <!-- Same classes work in both modes -->
</div>
```

## Animation Classes

```html
<!-- Fade in on scroll (use with Intersection Observer) -->
<div class="opacity-0 translate-y-4 transition-all duration-300 ease-out
            data-[visible=true]:opacity-100 data-[visible=true]:translate-y-0">

<!-- Hover lift -->
<div class="hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-150">
```
